' в•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ
' INGESTION PIPELINE
' в•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ
package "Ingestion Pipeline  (ingestion_pipeline.py)" #E9F7EF {

  component "Step 1 вЂ” PDF Parser\n(pdf_parser.py / pdfplumber)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\npdfplumber в†’ [{page_num, text}]\nget_full_text() в†’ single string\nchunk_pages():\n  CHUNK_SIZE = 3200 chars\n  CHUNK_OVERLAP = 400 chars\n  majority-vote page tracking\nв†’ chunks for ChromaDB\nв†’ full_text for extraction" as pdf_parser

  component "Step 1b вЂ” Formulary Truncation\n(claude_extractor.get_relevant_text)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\ndoc_type == formulary_book:\n  scan lines for drug_hint\n  return В±2вЂ“5 lines per hit\n  240-page book в†’ ~50 lines\nOther doc types: full text\n(prevents token bloat)" as formulary_filter

  component "Step 2 вЂ” Claude Extractor\n(claude_extractor.py)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nbatch_text_for_extraction()\n  60,000 chars per batch\nload prompt v2.0 from registry:\n  payer | drug | doc_type\n  benefit_side context vars\nformat_map(defaultdict) в†’\n  unknown placeholders в†’ \"\"\nJSON retry on decode error\ndeduplicate by generic_name" as extractor

  component "Step 3 вЂ” ChromaDB Embedder\n(embeddings.py)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nDefaultEmbeddingFunction\n(sentence-transformers/\n  all-MiniLM-L6-v2, 384-dim)\ncosine similarity space\ndelete old chunks first\nchroma_id = doc{id}_chunk{i}\nmetadata: plan_id, plan_name,\n  quarter, page_number" as embedder

  component "Step 4 вЂ” Structured Write\n(crud.py)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nget_or_create_drug()\nchange detection vs prior\nupsert_coverage_policy()\n  + benefit_side\n  + data_completeness\n  + benefit_side_note\nadd_prior_auth_criteria()\nadd_step_therapy()\nupsert_quantity_limit()       в†ђ NEW\nupsert_step_therapy_by_indication() в†ђ NEW" as structured_write

  component "Ingestion\nOrchestrator\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nReads doc.doc_type\ndoc.drug_hint\ndoc.benefit_side_hint\nWires steps 1вЂ“5\nStores prompt_version_id\non every CoveragePolicy\nCalls Hook B + Hook C" as pipeline

  core_api --> pipeline : document_id
  pipeline --> pdf_parser
  pdf_parser --> formulary_filter : full_text\n+ doc_type + drug_hint
  formulary_filter --> extractor : relevant_text
  extractor --> embedder : original chunks\n(full doc, not truncated)
  extractor --> structured_write : drugs[] JSON
  embedder --> structured_write : chroma_ids
}

