package "в‘Ў LLM Observability  (llm_logger.py)" #FDEDEC {
  component "tracked_call() wrapper\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nWraps client.messages.create()\ncall_type: extraction |\n  extraction_retry | intent |\n  rag_generation\nRecords: input_tokens,\n  output_tokens, latency_ms\nComputes cost in-process:\n  sonnet-4-6: $3/M in, $15/M out\nWrites to separate DB session\n(always commits, even on error)" as llm_logger
