  component "Layer 2 вЂ” SQL Pre-filter\n(crud.get_coverage_for_drug)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nDrug lookup: ilike match\nJOIN: CoveragePolicy\n  + HealthPlan + Drug\n  + PolicyDocument\nReturns: benefit_side,\n  data_completeness,\n  benefit_side_note,\n  PA criteria list,\n  step therapy drugs list" as sql_filter

  component "route_query() Decision\n(claude_rag.route_query)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nTier 1 if:\n  query_type in {coverage_check,\n    prior_auth, step_therapy}\n  AND drug_name present\n  AND structured_rows not empty\nTier 2 if:\n  structured_rows not empty\nTier 3: otherwise" as router

  component "Tier 1 вЂ” Structured Answer\n(_build_tier1_answer)\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nNo ChromaDB call\nNo Claude generation call\nRenders human-readable prose:\n  coverage status, benefit side,\n  PA criteria, step therapy,\n  quantity limit, source note\nsource_cost = $0.00\nrouting_tier = tier_1_structured" as tier1

